OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA murky start with extensive
OL,6,Flow cloud, although cloud tending to
OL,7,Flift slowly into the afternoon inland,
OL,8,Fwith some limited brightness possible
OL,9,Fin the south later. Slightly milder
OL,10,Fthan on Saturday for most. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud tending to lower
OL,13,Fovernight with mist, patchy fog and
OL,14,Fhill fog becoming more widespread
OL,15,Fagain. Winds remaining generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
